body.description: Instantly create writing space in binders and folders, by inserting the Spiral-Bound 1-Subject Notebook. Perfect for students and professionals, these notebooks feature a durable cover that helps protect the content written on the pages inside. Wide ruled format: the bright white paper has blue handwriting lines with a red margin divider to allow for neat writing. Solid colored front cover adds style to notebooks, while also making it easy to organize projects or classes by color. Attach this 3-hole punched spiral notebook into a standard 3-ring binder to create the ultimate organizational tool that keeps all your notes and hand-outs in one place. Perforated edges reduce paper waste by allowing pages to tear out neatly. 70-page spiral bound notebook. Colored front cover, gray board back cover. Green. Sold individually.
